Guess the output for the following program:

int fun(int x, int n) {
    if (n == 0)
        return 1;
    else if (n % 2 == 0)
        return fun(x * x, n / 2);
    else
        return x * fun(x * x, (n - 1) / 2);
}
int main() {
    int ans = fun(2, 10);
    printf("%d", ans);
    return 0;
}


Choose the correct answer from below:
1023
2048
1024
None of these

Answer : 1024
